#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "More Locations"
msgstr "更多地點"

#. ~ Description for More Locations
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds new Z-level buildings and dungeons, including apartment towers with "
"refugees along with bandits, estates, factories, towers, military outposts."
"  Though, a little bit unpolished, but made with plenty of effort.  Before "
"generating a world, you can remove subfolders to nix unwanted locations."
msgstr ""
"添加新的Z層級建築和地下城，包括帶有難民以及強盜的公寓塔樓、莊園、工廠、塔樓、軍事前哨。雖然略顯粗糙，但付出了大量努力。在生成世界之前，你可以移除子文件夾以排除不需要的地點。"

