#: .\captive_faction\TALK_CAPTIVE.json
msgid "Are you part of the rescue team?"
msgstr "你是救援隊的一員嗎？"

#: .\captive_faction\TALK_CAPTIVE.json
msgid "Sorry, <sass>, the rescue has been delayed."
msgstr "抱歉，<sass>，救援已經延遲了。"

#: .\captive_faction\TALK_CAPTIVE.json
msgid "Part?  I AM the rescue team."
msgstr "一員？我就是救援隊。"

#: .\captive_faction\TALK_CAPTIVE.json
msgid "So are you busting us out of here or what?"
